ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Depending on their interests I would recommend it.

I would recommend this course to students who are interested in theories of contemporary architecture. I have found that other courses in the "theory" of architecture are really just courses in history. That is to say, they do not focus on the social and cultural issues affecting art and architecture.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Exposed me to theory different to that which I am used to, helpful as a modernist

This course did deepen my knowledge of architecture, my discipline/profession. The course allowed me to explore subjects and issues that I had some curiosity. The course also introduced me to subjects of which I had little knowledge.
